query:
/*+  */ select count(*)
from question AS q
inner join tag_question AS tq
on tq.question_id = q.id AND q.score >= 0 AND q.score <= 0
inner join site AS s
on tq.site_id = s.site_id AND q.site_id = s.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('askubuntu')
inner join tag AS t
on tq.tag_id = t.id AND t.site_id = s.site_id AND t.name IN ('11.10',
'apache2',
'dependencies',
'gnome',
'internet',
'java',
'keyboard',
'kubuntu',
'network-manager',
'python',
'virtualbox',
'xubuntu');
